											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Dark Urge starts out walking upright, but as the next three narrator nodes go on and they get further into the darkness of the sewers, they get more and more crouched, like they've forgotten how to be a humanoid. ALTERNATIVE: they start to walk away, but as their urge drives them on, they begin to jog and then run, getting more excited and compelled" />
